getAirportsWithinRadius

public TreeSet<AirportDistance> getAirportsWithinRadius(LatLng position,
                                                        double radius,
                                                        int minRank)
                                                 throws InterruptedException
Returns airports within radius meters of position.

Retrieves all airports in a rectangular region bouding the search area using AirportDirectory.getAirportsInRectangle(com.google.flightmap.common.data.LatLngRect, int), and then filters out outliers.

Airport ranks are at least minRank.
Results are sorted in order of increasing distance from position.

Specified by:
getAirportsWithinRadius in interface AirportDirectory
Parameters:
position - Center of radius search
radius - Radius of search [meters]
minRank - Minimum airport rank to return
Throws:
InterruptedException
